# Sandgarden Prompts
- Prompts are templates for sending messages to LLMs
- Prompts are mustache templates
- The raw text of a prompt can be retrieved using the sandgarden runtime `sandgarden.get_prompt('prompt-name')`
- The prompt can be rendered as a template using `sandgarden.render_prompt('prompt-name', {"var": "value", "var2": "value"})`
